1
00:00:11,400 --> 00:00:12,160
Ms. Xu

2
00:00:12,439 --> 00:00:13,679
It looks like something happened to your husband.

3
00:00:14,320 --> 00:00:15,839
Do you want to go out and check?

4
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:16,879
No way.

5
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:19,160
Are you sure you aren't mistaken?

6
00:00:19,440 --> 00:00:20,640
What if it's true?

7
00:00:20,960 --> 00:00:22,199
The police are already here.

8
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:24,160
You'd better go out and take a look.

9
00:00:24,480 --> 00:00:25,440
I'm tired.

10
00:00:25,839 --> 00:00:27,079
I don't want to get involved.

11
00:00:27,559 --> 00:00:28,600
Go see for yourself.

12
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:30,800
Okay.

13
00:01:05,120 --> 00:01:05,760
Hey, mister.

14
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,439
Why are you losing your cool?

15
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:10,159
She isn't even jealous yet,

16
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:11,439
and you're already jealous.

17
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:14,079
I'm not losing my cool.

18
00:01:14,640 --> 00:01:15,719
Let me take you back to rest.

19
00:01:15,719 --> 00:01:16,959
Thanks, thank you.

20
00:01:17,079 --> 00:01:18,760
She's burning with jealousy now.

21
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,920
Push a little harder.

22
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:22,519
I guarantee she'll be head over heels for you.

23
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,640
Aren't you afraid that later

24
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:28,319
I'll start playing for real?

25
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:30,959
Bring it on.

26
00:01:35,079 --> 00:01:36,040
Let me tell you,

27
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:38,040
I really want to see

28
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,519
tonight,

29
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:41,159
who lets loose more.

30
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,680
A Zhen and A Qiang

31
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:53,400
are seasoned honey trap pros.

32
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:54,920
Who knows how many people they've victimized.

33
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:56,879
I wonder if they'll succeed tonight.

34
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,719
Bring your body cams.

35
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,159
With habitual offenders like them,

36
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,000
we have to catch them in the act.

37
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,680
Ms. Xu, please slow down.

38
00:02:14,960 --> 00:02:15,759
Manager Yu.

39
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,680
I keep feeling like in this room,

40
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:19,680
there are eyes watching me.

41
00:02:20,120 --> 00:02:20,960
You don't have

42
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:21,919
any

43
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:24,319
hidden cameras here, do you?

44
00:02:24,319 --> 00:02:25,919
Ms. Xu, rest assured.

45
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,560
Our villa would absolutely never allow

46
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,879
hidden cameras to exist.

47
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:30,280
Can you guarantee that?

48
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:30,800
I guarantee it.

49
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,360
What if there are?

50
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:34,719
If there are, I'll take responsibility.

51
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:36,280
The villa's business is my business.

52
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:37,120
But

53
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,120
anything else...

54
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:41,360
Ms. Xu.

55
00:02:43,319 --> 00:02:44,159
I'm sorry, I'm sorry.

56
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,080
Wait.

57
00:02:45,840 --> 00:02:46,560
Don't go.

58
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,039
Are you okay?

59
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,400
Am I pretty?

60
00:03:00,599 --> 00:03:01,120
Yes, you're pretty.

61
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:03,280
You're a true beauty.

62
00:03:03,639 --> 00:03:04,840
Absolutely stunning.

63
00:03:05,439 --> 00:03:06,479
You men

64
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,120
all love beautiful women.

65
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:09,960
But beautiful women

66
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,000
will grow old too.

67
00:03:13,000 --> 00:03:13,479
No.

68
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,120
Even before they get old,

69
00:03:15,879 --> 00:03:17,159
you're already sick of them.

70
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:18,439
You

71
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:20,000
are like hunters.

72
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:21,919
The prey you desire

73
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,680
is always the next one.

74
00:03:24,800 --> 00:03:25,639
I'm not like that.

75
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:27,400
I'm the type of guy

76
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,199
who's incredibly devoted.

77
00:03:30,039 --> 00:03:30,759
Really?

78
00:03:40,080 --> 00:03:41,360
Come on, mister!

79
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,039
I can barely run anymore.

80
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:52,039
Come on, mister!

81
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,199
Catch me,

82
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,759
and I'm all yours tonight.

83
00:03:54,759 --> 00:03:55,439
Hurry!

84
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,800
Alright.

85
00:03:57,639 --> 00:03:58,800
If a tiger doesn't show its teeth,

86
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,599
you'll take it for a sick cat, huh?

87
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,400
Hurry up!

88
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,319
Coming!

89
00:04:07,159 --> 00:04:07,599
Come here.

90
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:13,759
What's wrong?

91
00:04:14,840 --> 00:04:15,759
What's the matter?

92
00:04:15,759 --> 00:04:16,480
I feel terrible.

93
00:04:17,519 --> 00:04:19,000
Didn't we agree to film a video

94
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:20,240
to make your wife mad?

95
00:04:21,319 --> 00:04:23,040
Mister, what's wrong? Mister!

96
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,399
Pills... my pills.

97
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,519
What pills?

98
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:28,560
Are you okay?

99
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,279
Open it.

100
00:04:29,959 --> 00:04:30,480
Open it!

101
00:04:31,920 --> 00:04:32,319
Here.

102
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:33,800
Mister!

103
00:04:34,160 --> 00:04:35,120
Are you okay, mister?

104
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:36,639
Mister!

105
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:38,199
Mister!

106
00:04:38,199 --> 00:04:38,920
Help me lie down.

107
00:04:39,319 --> 00:04:39,800
Mister!

108
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:40,360
Help me lie down.

109
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:41,439
Don't scare me!

110
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:42,720
Mister!

111
00:04:43,519 --> 00:04:44,439
Mister!

112
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:47,800
Mister!

113
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:56,040
Someone's dead!

114
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,319
Someone's dead!

115
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:03,839
Somebody help!

116
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,680
Someone's dead!

117
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,120
Someone's dead!

118
00:05:20,560 --> 00:05:22,000
Help!

119
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:25,680
Help!

120
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:27,319
Someone's dead!

121
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:31,439
A Qiang! A Qiang! A Qiang!

122
00:05:31,439 --> 00:05:32,959
Stop yelling! Just run!

123
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:37,160
Freeze!

124
00:05:37,399 --> 00:05:38,240
What are you doing?

125
00:05:41,439 --> 00:05:42,399
Take it easy!

126
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:43,480
Get down!

127
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:44,720
Hands behind your head!

128
00:05:46,639 --> 00:05:47,240
Be gentle, would you?

129
00:05:47,240 --> 00:05:47,839
Behave!

130
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:48,680
Ouch, that hurts!

131
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,439
It wasn't me!

132
00:05:49,839 --> 00:05:50,360
What's going on?

133
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:51,439
What's the situation?

134
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:52,480
Holy crap.

135
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,120
Another dead body!

136
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,800
Police investigation! Step back!

137
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:56,560
It wasn't me!

138
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:57,639
Get down, now!

139
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,079
Watch the hair!

140
00:06:05,839 --> 00:06:06,439
Don't move!

141
00:06:07,839 --> 00:06:08,480
Call for backup!

142
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:11,199
Homicide at Clear Spring Villa.

143
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:11,879
Requesting backup.

144
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,279
Clear Spring Villa, homicide.

145
00:06:13,279 --> 00:06:14,040
Requesting backup.

146
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:14,800
Brother Hui.

147
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,199
A Zhen and A Qiang got locked up.

148
00:06:16,439 --> 00:06:17,360
But don't worry.

149
00:06:17,560 --> 00:06:19,120
They'll never rat you out.

150
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,519
In this world,

151
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,279
only dead men can be trusted.

152
00:06:23,480 --> 00:06:25,079
Since A Qiang's line is cut,

153
00:06:25,360 --> 00:06:26,480
the business on our end,

154
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,160
you'd better keep a close eye on it.

155
00:06:28,639 --> 00:06:30,000
A few guys still owe us money.

156
00:06:30,639 --> 00:06:31,800
It's time to teach them a lesson.

157
00:06:33,680 --> 00:06:34,319
Brother Hui.

158
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,639
Didn't we agree not to meet during the day?

159
00:06:42,040 --> 00:06:42,800
Why are you here?

160
00:06:44,439 --> 00:06:45,000
Well...

161
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,720
There's been another death at the villa.

162
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,600
I'd actually met the guy.

163
00:06:48,959 --> 00:06:50,000
I don't know why,

164
00:06:50,959 --> 00:06:52,279
but I feel terrible about it.

165
00:06:52,399 --> 00:06:52,920
Qiqi.

166
00:06:53,639 --> 00:06:55,399
Life is like a train ride.

167
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:57,879
Some people just get off earlier, that's all.

168
00:06:58,319 --> 00:07:00,720
Just keep your mind on your destination.

169
00:07:01,079 --> 00:07:01,600
Which is,

170
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:03,480
finding the documents as soon as possible,

171
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,319
and mortgaging the villa.

172
00:07:04,839 --> 00:07:06,560
Only then can we be truly free.

173
00:07:09,040 --> 00:07:10,959
A guaranteed loan went bad,

174
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:12,360
and we can't pay it off.

175
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:14,000
My place is going to get seized.

176
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:18,800
Don't worry.

177
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:20,319
I'll definitely help you.

178
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,160
That's my good Qiqi.

179
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:27,079
Old Wang's health

180
00:07:27,879 --> 00:07:29,360
has always been pretty good.

181
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:31,399
A perfectly healthy man,

182
00:07:32,759 --> 00:07:33,879
how could he just be gone?

183
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:35,519
Boss.

184
00:07:37,680 --> 00:07:39,120
Don't get so worked up.

185
00:07:39,439 --> 00:07:40,319
Have some coffee.

186
00:07:40,839 --> 00:07:42,680
Who knows which deity up there

187
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,120
we managed to offend.

188
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,639
One case after another.

189
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:47,120
The guests have all been scared off.

190
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:49,199
How are we supposed to do business?

191
00:07:49,199 --> 00:07:50,560
But don't be upset yet.

192
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,959
I've already asked around.

193
00:07:51,959 --> 00:07:54,079
The coroner has already ruled

194
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:55,079
that Wang Kechen

195
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:56,639
died of a heart attack.

196
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,040
The police also ruled

197
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,160
his death as an accident.

198
00:07:59,519 --> 00:08:00,800
It has nothing to do with our villa.

199
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:03,160
Boss Bai!

200
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,759
Ma'am.

201
00:08:07,879 --> 00:08:09,360
A perfectly healthy man

202
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,920
died right here in your villa.

203
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:13,040
And you're trying to dodge responsibility?

204
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:14,720
I'm going to sue you!

205
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,639
Please, don't get worked up.

206
00:08:16,639 --> 00:08:17,600
We can talk this through.

207
00:08:18,040 --> 00:08:19,079
Whatever your demands are,

208
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:20,199
just say the word.

209
00:08:20,439 --> 00:08:22,040
This is a human life we're talking about.

210
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,000
No amount of money

211
00:08:23,279 --> 00:08:24,839
can bring my husband back.

212
00:08:25,879 --> 00:08:27,240
So, what are you saying?

213
00:08:28,439 --> 00:08:29,759
Do I look like I need money?

214
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,080
Five million.

215
00:08:32,919 --> 00:08:34,120
Not a cent less.

216
00:08:43,279 --> 00:08:45,360
I really am innocent.

217
00:08:45,919 --> 00:08:46,759
Boss Wang...

218
00:08:47,159 --> 00:08:49,159
I wasn't the one who killed him.

219
00:08:50,360 --> 00:08:51,159
Stop crying!

220
00:08:51,559 --> 00:08:52,879
Now you're crying after he's dead?

221
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,200
You still have a chance right now.

222
00:08:54,639 --> 00:08:55,759
Explain to us clearly,

223
00:08:55,759 --> 00:08:56,960
what exactly did you do to him?

224
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:59,000
I didn't do anything.

225
00:08:59,240 --> 00:09:01,559
He wanted to test if his wife still loved him.

226
00:09:01,559 --> 00:09:03,279
I just played along with the act.

227
00:09:03,440 --> 00:09:04,320
Who knew...

228
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:05,799
We hadn't even entered the room.

229
00:09:05,919 --> 00:09:07,159
Nothing had happened yet.

230
00:09:07,279 --> 00:09:08,879
He suddenly collapsed.

231
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:09,600
Officer,

232
00:09:10,200 --> 00:09:11,120
could I get a cigarette?

233
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,639
Even a leaf would do if you don't have one.

234
00:09:15,279 --> 00:09:17,159
Since you've been tailing us, you'd know

235
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,519
A Zhen and I run honey traps.

236
00:09:19,519 --> 00:09:20,440
We're only after money,

237
00:09:20,919 --> 00:09:21,720
not lives.

238
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,720
If we killed our marks,

239
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,320
who'd pay us, right?

240
00:09:25,679 --> 00:09:26,600
So you admit

241
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:28,039
that you and A Zhen

242
00:09:28,279 --> 00:09:29,360
seduced Wang Kechen

243
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,200
to blackmail him?

244
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:32,799
Right?

245
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:34,200
Officer,

246
00:09:35,159 --> 00:09:36,799
why so serious?

247
00:09:36,799 --> 00:09:37,919
Isn't it trendy now

248
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,639
to enforce the law with a smile?

249
00:09:41,159 --> 00:09:41,759
That's right.

250
00:09:42,879 --> 00:09:44,600
The original plan was

251
00:09:44,600 --> 00:09:46,320
A Zhen lures that horny old geezer

252
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:47,720
into the room,

253
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,000
I burst in to scare him,

254
00:09:49,159 --> 00:09:49,879
grab the money and leave.

255
00:09:50,200 --> 00:09:51,120
But who knew,

256
00:09:51,440 --> 00:09:53,639
the geezer kicked the bucket before even getting to the room.

257
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,559
The things I did,

258
00:09:56,039 --> 00:09:56,600
I'll admit to.

259
00:09:57,039 --> 00:09:58,039
But murder?

260
00:09:58,320 --> 00:09:59,360
I didn't do it.

261
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,120
I won't admit to that.

262
00:10:00,799 --> 00:10:02,320
Since you started working with A Qiang,

263
00:10:02,600 --> 00:10:04,240
how many honey trap victims have there been?

264
00:10:04,879 --> 00:10:06,200
I don't remember clearly.

265
00:10:06,799 --> 00:10:09,320
A Qiang was in charge of the whole process.

266
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,320
Do you have any records?

267
00:10:11,639 --> 00:10:12,840
The law stipulates

268
00:10:13,159 --> 00:10:14,679
that voluntarily confessing your crimes,

269
00:10:14,960 --> 00:10:16,840
or exposing the crimes of others,

270
00:10:17,159 --> 00:10:18,399
once verified as true,

271
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:20,360
can be grounds for a lighter sentence.

272
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,080
If I talk,

273
00:10:22,279 --> 00:10:23,799
A Qiang will beat me to death.

274
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,000
That won't happen.

275
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:27,120
The police will protect your safety.

276
00:10:27,360 --> 00:10:29,480
What if I get a heavier sentence?

277
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:32,879
Even if you don't talk,

278
00:10:33,279 --> 00:10:34,679
we'll find out sooner or later.

279
00:10:35,159 --> 00:10:36,279
In our investigations,

280
00:10:36,600 --> 00:10:37,360
we look at evidence,

281
00:10:37,759 --> 00:10:38,639
and at attitude.

282
00:10:39,159 --> 00:10:40,480
Coming clean early

283
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:43,480
is better than having no chances left at all.

284
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:45,159
Actually,

285
00:10:45,919 --> 00:10:48,440
A Qiang would always pose as a repairman,

286
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,799
sneak into the target's room beforehand,

287
00:10:51,840 --> 00:10:53,720
and plant hidden cameras.

288
00:10:54,840 --> 00:10:56,519
Mainly to get a feel for

289
00:10:56,720 --> 00:10:57,840
the target's situation.

290
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,480
Just to get a feel for it?

291
00:11:01,320 --> 00:11:02,840
After busting them at the honey trap scene,

292
00:11:03,000 --> 00:11:04,120
you'd extort them once,

293
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:06,159
you'd use the video to extort them again later,

294
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:07,120
or even more.

295
00:11:08,919 --> 00:11:10,720
That was all A Qiang's doing.

296
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,600
I'm a victim too.

297
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:14,919
He'd beat me if I didn't cooperate.

298
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,919
It's obvious the suspect, A Qiang,

299
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,039
placed the pinhole camera

300
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,960
in the central AC vent,

301
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,519
connected it to the hotel's Wi-Fi,

302
00:11:37,279 --> 00:11:38,799
and set the secretly recorded videos

303
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:40,840
to automatically download onto this phone.

304
00:11:44,600 --> 00:11:45,159
That's right.

305
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:46,960
The latest video

306
00:11:47,159 --> 00:11:49,000
is from Wang Kechen and Xu Lingling's room.

307
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:21,039
Isn't that Yu Tianfang?

308
00:12:23,679 --> 00:12:24,879
It really is him.

309
00:12:25,399 --> 00:12:26,600
He's just a liar.

310
00:12:26,600 --> 00:12:27,720
When we went on a blind date,

311
00:12:27,720 --> 00:12:29,240
he said he already had someone he liked.

312
00:12:29,240 --> 00:12:31,320
But then he turns around and gets a room with another woman.

313
00:12:32,279 --> 00:12:33,879
And with such a huge age gap too.

314
00:12:34,759 --> 00:12:35,639
Men...

315
00:12:36,480 --> 00:12:37,399
Are all you men just...

316
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:38,080
We're on duty.

317
00:12:38,639 --> 00:12:39,399
Keep it professional.

318
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:52,960
Why is being a manager so hard?

319
00:12:55,320 --> 00:12:55,960
Yu Tianfang.

320
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:59,080
Officer Chu, Officer Qin.

321
00:12:59,360 --> 00:13:00,879
What exactly is your relationship with Xu Lingling?

322
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:03,759
What kind of relationship could we have?

323
00:13:03,759 --> 00:13:05,200
She's a guest at our villa.

324
00:13:05,440 --> 00:13:06,679
I just serve the guests, that's all.

325
00:13:07,639 --> 00:13:08,159
Oh, right.

326
00:13:08,360 --> 00:13:10,120
You haven't paid for that meal last time.

327
00:13:10,519 --> 00:13:11,679
I already paid at the front desk.

328
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:14,440
Oh, I didn't notice.

329
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,039
I've got work to do.

330
00:13:18,600 --> 00:13:20,039
That night, you and Xu Lingling...

331
00:13:20,039 --> 00:13:21,039
what exactly did you do?

332
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:23,600
Someone planted a camera in your room.

333
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:25,080
I've watched the entire video.

334
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,879
That was just a misunderstanding.

335
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:29,879
Yu Tianfang.

336
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,399
You still have a chance right now.

337
00:13:31,399 --> 00:13:33,240
Spill it, what exactly did you two do?

338
00:13:34,000 --> 00:13:35,759
That night, she was drunk,

339
00:13:36,279 --> 00:13:38,200
so I walked her back to her room.

340
00:13:38,919 --> 00:13:39,840
By accident,

341
00:13:40,559 --> 00:13:41,519
she pushed me over.

342
00:13:43,480 --> 00:13:44,039
Ms. Xu.

343
00:13:44,879 --> 00:13:45,720
I'm... I'm sorry.

344
00:13:45,720 --> 00:13:46,080
Ms. Xu.

345
00:13:46,080 --> 00:13:46,600
Wait.

346
00:13:47,440 --> 00:13:48,600
Are... are you okay?

347
00:13:49,279 --> 00:13:50,919
You're like hunters.

348
00:13:51,519 --> 00:13:53,000
The prey you desire

349
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:55,799
is always the next one.

350
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,000
I'm not like that.

351
00:13:59,000 --> 00:13:59,720
I'm the kind of guy

352
00:14:00,279 --> 00:14:00,879
who's incredibly devoted.

353
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:02,960
Really?

354
00:14:03,679 --> 00:14:04,919
Someone's dead!

355
00:14:05,279 --> 00:14:06,519
Somebody help!

356
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:13,759
What happened?

357
00:14:14,120 --> 00:14:14,840
What's going on?

358
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:15,960
Holy crap.

359
00:14:16,480 --> 00:14:17,399
Another dead body.

360
00:14:17,799 --> 00:14:19,279
Police investigation. Step back.

361
00:14:20,759 --> 00:14:21,360
Get down, now!

362
00:14:24,240 --> 00:14:25,799
I was scared out of my mind back then.

363
00:14:26,240 --> 00:14:27,200
Thinking back on it,

364
00:14:27,919 --> 00:14:30,000
that Xu Lingling is no ordinary woman.

365
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:32,600
She was extremely calm back then.

366
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:33,879
Tell me,

367
00:14:33,879 --> 00:14:35,879
what wife hears her husband's in trouble

368
00:14:35,879 --> 00:14:36,960
and isn't panicked at all?

369
00:14:37,559 --> 00:14:38,519
You were with her at the time.

370
00:14:38,519 --> 00:14:40,240
When she heard that her husband,

371
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:41,759
Wang Kechen, had died,

372
00:14:42,240 --> 00:14:44,240
do you remember how she reacted?

373
00:14:46,080 --> 00:14:46,679
She did cry,

374
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,200
but she didn't shed a single tear.

